high_descs: Move straight ahead to the fridge, then turn left and go to stand in front of the pan with a long handle on the kitchen island.
Pick up the pan from the island.
Turn around and carry the pan to the fridge.
Place the pan on the top shelf in the fridge, close the door, and then remove after a few seconds.
Turn left and carry the pan to the kitchen sink.
Place the pan in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a cold pan in the sink.

high_descs: Hang a left at the fridge and walk to the island counter on the left.
Pick up the silver pan in front of the head of lettuce on the counter.
Turn left and walk to the white fridge on the left.
Put the pan inside the fridge on the top shelf, chill it, remove it and close the door.
Turn left and walk to the sink on the right.
Put the chilled pan inside the sink on the right side.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled pan in a sink.

high_descs: Walk over to the fridge, the hang a left and walk forward, turn left to face the kitchen island.
Pick up the metal pan off of the kitchen island.
Turn left and walk over to the fridge.
Put the metal pan in the fridge and close the fridge door, after a couple seconds open the fridge and take the now chilled metal pan out then close the fridge again.
Turn left and walk towards the counter, then turn right to face the sink.
Put the chilled pan in the sink basin.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled pan in the sink.
